title: Spectacular Spider-Girl (2009) #12
description:
MARVEL DIGITAL COMICS EXCLUSIVE
When Harry Osborn returned to New York City and bought his old gang's hang out, the Coffee Bean, he was on top of the world.  But when a coffee chain opens across the street and begins stealing his customers, Harry gets a tough lesson in the street fight of modern business.  Lucky for him he's got one of the toughest street heroes in town on his side in Peter Parker, the Friendly Neighborhood Spider-Man!  But will the Parker luck rub off on the Coffee Bean? And What part does SCREWBALL play?  Joe Caramagna (IRON MAN & THE ARMOR WARS) and Todd Nauck (ASM583 -- Spidey Meets the President) take a stand for the little guy in "BARGAIN DONUTS"!
